        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownWhiterunFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionWhiterun\")",
        "content": "Hillgrund's Tomb is the Nordic burial chamber of the Hillgrund line — necromancers have raised the family draugr, and a descendant of that bloodline wants them put down.",
        "display_name": "Hillgrund's Tomb",
        "emotion": "",
        "importance": 0.65,
