        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownWhiterunFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionWhiterun\")",
        "content": "Valtheim Towers is a pair of stone towers spanning the White River east of Whiterun. Bandits hold the bridge and collect 'tolls' from anyone who tries to cross.",
        "display_name": "Valtheim Towers",
        "emotion": "",
